# AI Movie Recommender - Environment Configuration
# 
# QUICK START:
#   1. Copy this file to .env:  cp .env.example .env
#   2. Edit .env and fill in your API keys below
#   3. Run: docker-compose up -d
#   4. Access at: http://localhost:8097
#
# GETTING API KEYS:
#   TMDB: https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api (free, instant)
#   Jellyfin: Dashboard → Advanced → API Keys
#   Radarr/Sonarr: Settings → General → API Key
#
# NOTE: This is the ONLY file you need to create manually.
# All other files in data/ are auto-generated on first run.

# =============================================================================
# REQUIRED: TMDB API
# Get your API key from: https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
# This is used for movie metadata, recommendations, and posters
# =============================================================================
TMDB_API_KEY=your_tmdb_api_key_here

# =============================================================================
# REQUIRED: Jellyfin Integration
# Used to read your watch history and library
# =============================================================================
# Example: JELLYFIN_URL=http://192.168.1.100:8096
JELLYFIN_URL=http://your-jellyfin-server:8096
JELLYFIN_API_KEY=your_jellyfin_api_key_here

# =============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: Radarr Integration (for automatic movie downloads)
# =============================================================================
# Example: RADARR_URL=http://192.168.1.100:7878
RADARR_URL=http://your-radarr-server:7878
RADARR_API_KEY=your_radarr_api_key_here

# =============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: Sonarr Integration (for automatic TV show downloads)
# =============================================================================
# Example: SONARR_URL=http://192.168.1.100:8989
SONARR_URL=http://your-sonarr-server:8989
SONARR_API_KEY=your_sonarr_api_key_here

# =============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: HuggingFace Token
# Only needed if you have rate limiting issues with model downloads
# Get token from: https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
# =============================================================================
# HF_TOKEN=your_huggingface_token_here
